{
  "title": "AI Session Generation",
  "uid": "aigen-overview",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "tags": ["readmates", "aigen"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "provider",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(readmates_aigen_jobs_completed_total, provider)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*"
      },
      {
        "name": "model",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(readmates_aigen_jobs_completed_total{provider=~\"$provider\"}, model)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latency p50 / p95 / p99 by provider (s)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(readmates_aigen_latency_seconds_bucket{provider=~\"$provider\",model=~\"$model\"}[5m])) by (le, provider))",
          "legendFormat": "p50 {{provider}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(readmates_aigen_latency_seconds_bucket{provider=~\"$provider\",model=~\"$model\"}[5m])) by (le, provider))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{provider}}",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(readmates_aigen_latency_seconds_bucket{provider=~\"$provider\",model=~\"$model\"}[5m])) by (le, provider))",
          "legendFormat": "p99 {{provider}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Cost rate by provider/model (USD/s, 5m)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_cost_usd_total{provider=~\"$provider\",model=~\"$model\"}[5m])) by (provider, model)",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{model}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Top-N club cost (drill down via SQL)",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**`club_id` is intentionally not exported as a Prometheus label** (spec §11.1 — PII + cardinality).\n\nTop-N per-club cost is unavailable from Prometheus. Query the `ai_generation_audit_log` table instead:\n\n```sql\nSELECT\n  club_id,\n  SUM(cost_usd) AS total_cost,\n  COUNT(*) AS jobs\nFROM ai_generation_audit_log\nWHERE created_at >= now() - INTERVAL '30 days'\nGROUP BY club_id\nORDER BY total_cost DESC\nLIMIT 20;\n```\n\nSee the runbook (`docs/operations/runbooks/ai-session-generation.md`) for the canonical operator drill-down procedure."
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Validation failures by reason (5m rate)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_validation_failures_total[5m])) by (reason)",
          "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "normal" } } } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Queue lag (readmates_aigen_queue_depth)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "readmates_aigen_queue_depth",
          "legendFormat": "queue_depth",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16 }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Jobs by status/provider (5m rate)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_jobs_completed_total{provider=~\"$provider\",model=~\"$model\"}[5m])) by (status, provider)",
          "legendFormat": "{{status}} / {{provider}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "normal" } } } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16 }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Tokens by direction (5m rate)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_tokens_total{provider=~\"$provider\",model=~\"$model\"}[5m])) by (direction)",
          "legendFormat": "{{direction}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 24 }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Cap denials by reason (5m rate)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_cap_denials_total[5m])) by (reason)",
          "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 24 }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Provider call outcomes",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_provider_calls_total{provider=~\"$provider\"}[5m])) by (provider, status)",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 32 }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Provider call latency",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(readmates_aigen_provider_call_latency_seconds_bucket{provider=~\"$provider\"}[5m])) by (le, provider))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{provider}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 32 }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Cost basis",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_provider_cost_usd_total{provider=~\"$provider\"}[5m])) by (provider, basis)",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{basis}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 40 }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Gate rejections",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_aigen_provider_gate_rejections_total{provider=~\"$provider\"}[5m])) by (provider, reason)",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 40 }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Circuit state",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "resilience4j_circuitbreaker_state{name=~\"aigen-provider-(openai|claude|gemini)\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} / {{state}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 48 }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Exporter and Tempo health",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"tempo\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Tempo target",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_observability_otlp_export_spans_total{status=\"failed\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "OTLP failed spans/s",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(tempo_distributor_spans_received_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Tempo received spans/s",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(readmates_observability_otlp_queue_dropped_spans_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "OTLP queue dropped spans/s",
          "refId": "D"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 48 }
    }
  ]
}
